## â­ **Features**
- ğŸ¥ **Real-Time Webcam Feed:** The effect processes live video input from the webcam.
- ğŸ› ï¸ **Dynamic GUI Controls:** Adjust grid cell size, circle radius, and toggle fill status.
- ğŸ¨ **Color Channel Control:** Enable/disable individual RGB channels.
- ğŸ“± **Responsive Visuals:** Grid and circle size dynamically adapt to the selected parameters.

